   "source": [
    "## 5. Variance Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "Analyzing how much variance each principal component explains reveals the dimensionality of market dynamics."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 29,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
