    "## 10. Rolling Regime Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "Analyzing how regimes evolve over rolling windows provides insight into market dynamics."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 38,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
